{"tid":6464,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"依加d 面飽真係好撚貴","createTime":"2016-11-27T11:19:08.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-27T18:50:06.000Z","uid":22927,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"185d1c44b6e194c45368ee8ff11f136e808673b7","tid":6464,"uid":22927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T11:19:08.000Z","msg":"今日收工見肚餓，係東涌地鐵站間美心買個腸仔飽，拎去排隊比錢果陣個面飽妹Mary話：多謝你九個六。<br />\n我即刻大叫：九個六！？大話骰呀。<br />\n之後一巴就煎落佢塊面到，煎到佢頭轉360，成個地鐵站靜晒，所有人都望晒過黎，之後佢一下除左自己條圍裙，兩隻手暗住自己塊面直奔出店外面，跑緊嘅時候仲隱約見到有d 閃閃令嘅淚珠飛出黎，突然一架巴士炒左上黎，撞到個女仔粉碎左，佢個人就好似七味粉咁散落一地，之後就落大雨，個女仔都比人沖左落渠。<br />\n我就繼續食腸仔飽，食食下就天黑，美心出面企左個男仔，係度不停望錶，不停口upup：又話今日收早，點解仲未放架。<br />\n我問佢：係咪等緊Mary。<br />\n佢話：係。<br />\n我話：Mary 比人沖左落渠喎。<br />\n佢即刻衝去個渠口，想抽起個渠蓋，但抽極都抽唔起。跟住隔離有個gym 妹遞左張刮刮卡比佢話：先生，你好似唔夠力wo，不如做gym 丫，依加做緊優惠呀。<br />\n佢見我係隔離睇，順手遞埋比我，我一睇，原來係成龍果間，我正想問佢：乜唔係執左啦咩？個男仔就屌佢話：做我都做城城果間啦！<br />\n<br />\n想問返咁多位成龍果間好定城城果間好，我刮到買十二年送十二年，做唔做好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cecd5450c37323d84959d71866ba46707a12ee2","tid":6464,"uid":531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T11:21:53.000Z","msg":"上次成龍果間offer20+20<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3753588f4ec75d4dd0c4ac31ddbaa82bae35715f","tid":6464,"uid":12421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T11:22:47.000Z","msg":"張信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ac0a5d06bc6932d7aa1be020e9226334fd835b4","tid":6464,"uid":22927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T11:24:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上次成龍果間offer20+20<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁做唔做好，聽日過期啦，好想練到舉得起個渠蓋"},{"pid":"9ec305f9120bb6c7ad2591683f559ab4f2e4277e","tid":6464,"uid":2383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T11:25:58.000Z","msg":"即係五粒魚蛋幾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75b3d9661c2bf98e44874bb220d90a82b0ac1f98","tid":6464,"uid":22927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T11:27:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>即係五粒魚蛋幾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n魚蛋要落七味粉喎"},{"pid":"8af04709facd08323b4e74d43fc60120d266960d","tid":6464,"uid":25112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T11:27:37.000Z","msg":"無是咁的 重作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0715a412499322bc024ce1026b315f11145479af","tid":6464,"uid":22927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T11:29:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無是咁的 重作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真人真事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"790dbf88edd60afcc0a69b43edd04efbcba69f26","tid":6464,"uid":3119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T11:34:40.000Z","msg":"你買左個咩包"},{"pid":"162509446bb7d2e39bdd3ba6c478476b24089f0b","tid":6464,"uid":22927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T11:42:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你買左個咩包</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n腸仔包囉，九個六呀！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8273b99f1b42031b8bdd80eaf156ee7456ac60e","tid":6464,"uid":6518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T18:31:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你買左個咩包</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n腸仔包囉，九個六呀！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大你十個一"},{"pid":"1fdfa7ee6267eb16ed926a75246308345f16fa79","tid":6464,"uid":4725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T18:50:06.000Z","msg":"腸仔飽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" c